; Promptless best-of-three from the standard library.
;
; Three attempts fire (concurrently under the parallel evaluator); the
; symbol judge mediates deterministically — the answer that best
; round-trips onto {staged, rollback, plan} wins, and no model call is
; spent on judging.
;
;   kaos rebis run examples/best-of.rebis
(
  (# std/spread)
  (# std/shape)
  (best-of-three staged-rollback-plan
    (final-only "Write a staged rollback plan for the billing migration.")))
